@1lovetennis Dear @1lovetennis thank you for choosing Korean Air. Unfortunately, our twitter account only can help simple issues. Kindly contact our service center for ticketing inquiries. 

*Service center : https://t.co/7nab57X56C

*Chatbot/Livechat : https://t.co/EBl1vtRIs3

@tronprogram2 Dear @tronprogram2 , hello. Than you for choosing Korean Air. You can request to send the e-mail through our service center. Kindly contact us for assistance.

*Service center : https://t.co/7nab57X56C
*Chatbot/livechat : https://t.co/EBl1vtRIs3

@juheenuna Dear @juheenuna thank you for choosing Korean Air. Unfortunately, our twitter account only can help simple issues. Kindly contact our service center or chatbot livechat for SkyPass inquiries. 

*Service center : https://t.co/7nab57X56C
*Chatbot/livechat : https://t.co/EBl1vtRIs3

@benedictvillas The ticket name must be same with passport name. If you want to change the names(reservation, SkyPass), kindly contact our service center or your travel agency.

*Contact number : https://t.co/7nab57X56C
*Chatbot : https://t.co/EBl1vtRIs3 (and type 'live chat')

@dsweetestHoney Dear honey francisco, hello. As fas as I know, only passport represents a passenger's nationality. For detailed information, please contact Korean Govt or Embassy.

Kindly refer to Korean Govt. website https://t.co/Y7OOYiB9fR

and K-ETA website https://t.co/9oT1qrDyfo

@avrieloy Dear @avrieloy , hello. Thank you for contacting us.

As I see your tracking number, I can not define whether the package is carried by Korean Air. https://t.co/tg5sc04ceI

Due to pandemic, it is known that general delay of cargo is caused often. Kindly wait for further update.

@Roxyskywilliams Dear Roxy, hello. Thank you for choosing Korean Air. Our reservation staff may check you out.

To contact our service center, kindly search the number on this page : https://t.co/kYHrvpyQma

or enter chatbot to call our staff :  https://t.co/RVdKMYoGqq (and type 'live chat')
